      "date": "2012-03-02 06:09:34.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 5: Looks good to me, approved\n\nPer Shadow's comment in LU-1039, an equivalent patch been landed on 1.4.12, 1.6.1, and 1.8 (commit a5e24b1d22) since 2007, but was somehow missed from the master branch.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
